description:
Update frontend/src/app.css with neo-brutalist design tokens.

## Files
- Modify: frontend/src/app.css

## Changes
Replace current CSS variables with:
```css
:root {
  /* Light mode */
  --bg-primary: #f5f3f0;
  --bg-secondary: #ffffff;
  --bg-tertiary: #ebe8e4;
  --text-primary: #1a1a1a;
  --text-secondary: #555555;
  --text-muted: #888888;
  --border-color: #1a1a1a;

  /* Accent colors - Tailwind 500 */
  --amber: #f59e0b;
  --emerald: #10b981;
  --sky: #0ea5e9;
  --violet: #8b5cf6;
  --rose: #f43f5e;

  /* Shadows */
  --shadow: 3px 3px 0 var(--border-color);
  --shadow-hover: 5px 5px 0 var(--border-color);
  --shadow-sm: 2px 2px 0 var(--border-color);

  /* Borders */
  --border: 2px solid var(--border-color);
  --border-light: 1px solid var(--border-color);

  /* Radius */
  --radius: 8px;
  --radius-lg: 12px;
  --transition: 0.15s ease;
  --sidebar-width: 250px;
}

[data-theme="dark"] {
  --bg-primary: #1a1a1a;
  --bg-secondary: #0a0a0a;
  --bg-tertiary: #111111;
  --text-primary: #f5f5f5;
  --text-secondary: #a0a0a0;
  --text-muted: #606060;
  --border-color: #000000;
}
```

Also add Outfit font import and base body styles.
